<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM41.2">
<l>uymmiṉ ṟiṟaikoṇarn teṉṟula kāṇṭava rimmaiyē</l>
<l>tammiṉ cuvaimaṭa vāraippiṟar koḷḷat tāmviṭṭu</l>
<l>vemmi ṉoḷiveyil kāṉakam pōykkumai tiṉparkaḷ</l>
<l>cemmiṉ muṭittiru mālai viraintaṭi cērmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Be saved! Those who fetch tribute, speak [and] rule the world in this birth,</l>
<l>they will let go of their tasty women for others to take,</l>
<l>go into the forest with hot, flashing, bright sunlight [and] be thrashed.</l>
<l>Hastily join the feet of Tirumāl with a red-flashing crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
